rcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一部新的纪录片《<i>从昨天开始：苏格兰女子乐队不为人知的故事</i>》将揭示苏格兰过去 50 年来最伟大的无名女子组合。</p><p>这部长篇电影将于 10 月 18 日起在英国影院上映，届时英国许多最具开拓性、另类的女性流行音乐和独立艺术家将发表自己的声音，记录她们在男性主导的行业中的反抗和突破创新。几十年来。放映门票可<a href="http://sinceyesterdayfilm.com/lander" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到。</p><p>这部电影由音乐家、格拉斯哥和谐乐队 TeenCanteen 前成员卡拉·J·伊斯顿 (Carla J. Easton) 编剧和导演，联合导演布莱尔·杨 (Blair Young) 曾为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/belle-and-sebastian">Belle &amp; Sebastian</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/teenage-fanclub">Teenage Fanclub</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/biffy-clyro">Biffy Clyro</a>制作过视频。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="2024 年 DOC&#39;N ROLL |从昨天开始苏格兰女子乐队不为人知的故事 - 预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VOYYmM7e0sw?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <i>《Yesterday》</i>将讲述麦金利乐队 (The McKinleys) 的崛起，这是第一支苏格兰女子乐队，于 1964 年凭借单曲《甜蜜而温柔的浪漫》(Sweet and Tender Romance) 获得排行榜上的成功，并将吸收诸如草莓弹簧刀 (Strawberry Switchblade) 等团体的影响力（影片的片名正是由其标志性歌曲命名） 、 精致的 Boom Boom、The Ettes、The Hedrons、他最新的 Flame、Hello Skinny、Lung Leg 和 Sunset Gun。</p><p>该片于上个月在爱丁堡国际电影节闭幕式上进行了全球首映，并将于 10 月 18 日在格拉斯哥的首映之夜进行特别放映，并在 Mono 举办一晚的映后演出，并由 Sophisticated Boom Boom 重制一晚只为特殊的表演。麦金利乐队 (McKinleys) 的珍妮特·加拉格尔 (Jeanette Gallagher)、歌曲创作团体 Hen Hoose 和 This Mortal Coil 的路易斯·鲁特科斯基 (Louise Rutkowski) 也将在活动中表演。 </p><figure id="attachment_3797510" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3797510" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3797510" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3797510" class="wp-caption-text"> 《从昨天开始》海报。图片来源：宇宙猫</figcaption></figure><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="麦金利一家 - “甜蜜而温柔的浪漫” 1964" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8MzmzqZJQjQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="草莓弹簧刀——从昨天开始" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/x7QPBzAJ_io?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>伊斯顿谈到这个项目时说道：“自从我第一次向布莱尔提出制作一部关于 2016 年在苏格兰组建乐队的女性历史的纪录片的想法以来，我们一直很高兴能让观众听到我们所有的伟大音乐。已经知道了，然后是我们随后发现的所有音乐。但更重要的是，它让人们听到那些创作音乐的女性讲述她们的故事的经历，这是她们以前从未真正有机会做的事情。”</p><p>杨补充道：“我很高兴人们能够在电影中以及通过与放映和其他活动一起发生的现场活动来听到这种音乐并认识这些令人惊叹的角色，我希望它能在某种程度上帮助改变一些事情。”未来的乐队。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/new-music-doc-to-tell-story-of-scotlands-unsung-girl-bands-3797509">讲述苏格兰无名女子乐队故事的新音乐纪录片</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
流媒体服务 TikTok Music 即将关闭https://www.nme.com/news/music/streaming-service-tiktok-music-is-shutting-down-3797505?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=streaming-service-tiktok-music-is-shutting-downLaura Molloy Thu, 26 Sep 2024 20:26:29 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3797505 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该服务推出仅一年多</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/streaming-service-tiktok-music-is-shutting-down-3797505">流媒体服务 TikTok Music 关闭的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TikTok.-CREDIT_-Photo-illustration-by-Chesnot_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/tiktok">TikTok</a>的流媒体服务 TikTok Music 在运营仅一年多后即将关闭。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tiktok-unveil-songs-of-the-summer-2024-3784965">TikTok 推出“2024 年夏季之歌”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该平台宣布将于 11 月 28 日停止 TikTok Music 的运营。他们在官方网站上发布的一份声明中表示：“我们感谢大家的支持，希望你们喜欢这些音乐。”</p><p> TikTok Music <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tiktok-appears-to-be-planning-a-music-streaming-app-3281566">最初于 2022 年提出</a>，并于 2023 年 7 月推出，目前在印度尼西亚、巴西、澳大利亚、新加坡和墨西哥推出。</p><p> TikTok 音乐业务开发全球主管 Ole Obermann 告诉<a href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/tiktok-music-shutting-down-november/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard Pro</em></a> ，该应用程序将关闭流媒体服务，“以便专注于我们的目标，即进一步推动 TikTok 在推动更多音乐聆听和音乐流媒体服务价值方面的作用，为艺术家、歌曲作者和整个行业的利益。”</p><p>这包括 TikTok 的“添加到音乐”功能，该功能<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-tiktok-feature-will-allow-users-to-save-songs-directly-to-their-spotify-apple-music-and-more-3541478">于去年 11 月推出</a>，允许用户直接将应用程序中的声音保存到他们选择的流媒体平台。美国和英国的用户最初能够测试该功能，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tiktoks-add-to-music-app-feature-rolls-out-to-19-more-countries-3560060">在下个月将其推广到另外 19 个国家</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3600182" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3600182" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3600182" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TikTok-star-Leah-Smith.jpg" alt="抖音" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TikTok-star-Leah-Smith.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TikTok-star-Leah-Smith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TikTok-star-Leah-Smith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TikTok-star-Leah-Smith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TikTok-star-Leah-Smith-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TikTok-star-Leah-Smith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3600182" class="wp-caption-text"> TikTok 明星 Leah Smith 在 TikTok 上发布了她癌症治疗的最新信息。图片来源：Getty/Phil Barker 摄/Future Publishing via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>虽然 TikTok Music 似乎成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/spotify">Spotify</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/apple">Apple</a> Music 等现有流媒体服务的直接竞争对手，但奥伯曼表示，Add To Music 代表了“TikTok 上的发现与音乐流媒体服务消费之间的直接联系”，这使得它“比以往任何时候都更容易”让音乐迷可以在他们选择的音乐流媒体服务上欣赏完整长度的歌曲，从而为艺术家和权利持有者创造更大的价值。”</p><p>在此之前，该应用程序与音乐行业的关系不稳定，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/universal-music-group">环球音乐集团</a>(UMG) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/universal-pulling-music-from-tiktok-licensing-agreement-3579757">一月份从该平台撤回了其艺术家的音乐，因为双方在之前的协议到期后无法达成新的协议</a>。</p><p> UMG 声称，“TikTok 提议向我们的艺术家和词曲作者支付的费用只是类似情况的主要社交平台支付费用的一小部分”，据称这占其收入的 1%。</p><p>然而， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tiktok-and-universal-announce-new-chapter-with-music-to-return-to-streaming-under-new-agreement-3752603">两家公司在 5 月份宣布了“新篇章”，签订了新的许可协议</a>，据报道，该协议将“为 UMG 的歌曲作者和艺术家提供更高的报酬，为他们的唱片和歌曲提供新的促销和参与机会，并为他们提供行业领先的保护。”根据当时的新闻稿。</p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad0 id_ad_content-horiz-center">其他新闻方面， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tiktok-unveil-songs-of-the-summer-2024-3784965">TikTok 于 8 月宣布了他们的官方《Songs Of The Summer》</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Tinashe">Tinashe 的</a>《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jrjESdPsLxE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nasty</a> 》在英国排名第一，而全球冠军是 FloyyMenor 和 Cris Mj 的《Gata Only》。蒂娜什 (Tinashe) 也在全球榜单上名列第二。</div><div>其他进入英国排行榜前十名的歌曲包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>的《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1IUCyniCWzg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Birds Of A Feather》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a>的《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cF1Na4AIecM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Please Please Please</a> 》。</div><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/streaming-service-tiktok-music-is-shutting-down-3797505">流媒体服务 TikTok Music 关闭的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
