翻唱了彼此针对心理健康和无家可归者慈善机构的经典歌曲，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Tom-Clarke-of-The-Enemy-and-Billy-Lunn-of-The-Subways.-CREDIT_-Mark-Holloway_Redferns-and-Didier-Messens_Redferns.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Tom-Clarke-of-The-Enemy-and-Billy-Lunn-of-The-Subways.-CREDIT_-Mark-Holloway_Redferns-and-Didier-Messens_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Tom-Clarke-of-The-Enemy-and-Billy-Lunn-of-The-Subways.-CREDIT_-Mark-Holloway_Redferns-and-Didier-Messens_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Tom-Clarke-of-The-Enemy-and-Billy-Lunn-of-The-Subways.-CREDIT_-Mark-Holloway_Redferns-and-Didier-Messens_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Tom-Clarke-of-The-Enemy-and-Billy-Lunn-of-The-Subways.-CREDIT_-Mark-Holloway_Redferns-and-Didier-Messens_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Tom-Clarke-of-The-Enemy-and-Billy-Lunn-of-The-Subways.-CREDIT_-Mark-Holloway_Redferns-and-Didier-Messens_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Tom-Clarke-of-The-Enemy-and-Billy-Lunn-of-The-Subways.-CREDIT_-Mark-Holloway_Redferns-and-Didier-Messens_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-enemy">The Enemy</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-subways">The Subways</a>宣布他们将发行彼此热门歌曲的封面，为心理健康和无家可归者慈善机构筹集资金。请在下面找到更多详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-enemy-interview-tom-clarke-indie-sleaze-tour-new-music-holloways-subways-3772453">敌人：“独立肮脏？ ‘肮脏’不是贬义词吗？”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这些封面将于 10 月 10 日分享，以纪念世界心理健康日和世界无家可归者日。将为住房和无家可归者慈善机构<a href="https://www.shelter.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shelter</a>和心理健康慈善机构<a href="https://www.mind.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mind</a>筹集资金。</p><p> The Subways 将演绎《We’ll Live And Die InThese Towns》，而 The Enemy 则录制了他们演绎的《Rock &amp; Roll Queen》。</p><p>除了赛道之外，还将出售限量版围巾，为这两个慈善机构筹集资金。每购买一条围巾，就会额外捐赠一条空白围巾给慈善机构。它们将在乐队即将举行的现场演出中提供，或者您也可以<a href="https://ilovealcopop.co.uk/collections/the-subways/products/the-enemy-x-the-subways-half-and-half-charity-scarf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处在线预订</a>。</p><p>在此之前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-enemy-announce-2024-uk-tour-with-the-subways-the-holloways-buy-tickets-3609081">，The Enemy 即将于 10 月 4 日在爱丁堡举行“Indie Til I Die”英国巡演</a>。The Subways 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-holloways">The Holloways</a>都将作为特邀嘉宾加入。这三支独立乐队将在格拉斯哥、纽卡斯尔、曼彻斯特和伯明翰进行演出，然后于 10 月 19 日在伦敦结束演出。</p><p>门票现已发售，可<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-enemy-tickets%2Fartist%2F1159468" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处购买</a>。下面列出了完整的节目列表。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DAVSNtau2t6/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: